e\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: #3d5a3e; color: #fff; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px;\">加入 LINE 即時諮詢</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: #f9f6f0; padding: 20px 32px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e8dcc8;\">\n      <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; margin: 0;\">韻手作永續 Wishlite｜讓永續成為日常的美好行動</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
